      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].lines.Array.size
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.size
      value: 15
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[0].text
      value: Well, hello!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[1].text
      value: ' I''ve been waiting for you '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[2].text
      value: You have been waiting?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[3].text
      value: But how did you know that I was coming to you?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[4].text
      value: Well, I'm an all-wise wizard, I saw you in a magic ball
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[5].text
      value: Well, then you already know why I came to you?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[6].text
      value: You want me to become your mentor and teach you magic.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[7].text
      value: ' But I haven''t taken students for a long time, there were many applicants,
        but I didn''t see any potential in any of them.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[8].text
      value: I also wanted to refuse you, but I saw how you defeated the serpent,
        who was one with the very demons who abducted your brother.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[9].text
      value: SO IT MEANS THAT YOU AGREE TO BECOME MY MENTOR!?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[10].text
      value: ' I agree, but don''t think it will be easy. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[11].text
      value: 'Every time you learn a new spell, you will need to prove that you are
        worthy. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[12].text
      value: I will give you different tasks each time, and in doing them, you will
        have to be sent to different parts of our world. Are you ready for this?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[13].text
      value: Ready! Of course I'm ready!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[14].text
      value: All right, then follow me to my tower.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[0].onLineEnd.m_PersistentCalls.m_Calls.Array.size
